5
00:00:21,997 --> 00:00:25,157
And we are both game designers for a studio called Shell Games,

6
00:00:25,498 --> 00:00:29,079
and if you haven't heard of us, we're a studio that works on a wide variety of

7
00:00:29,199 --> 00:00:32,639
different weird things, both original IP and

8
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:33,160
client work.

9
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:37,704
But our most well-known VR title is probably I Expect You to Die.

10
00:00:37,924 --> 00:00:41,327
It's a kind of escape the room spy fi puzzler

11
00:00:41,787 --> 00:00:44,930
where you need to escape death defying situations that only a,

12
00:00:44,950 --> 00:00:48,412
you know, spy with telekinesis would find themselves in.

13
00:00:49,033 --> 00:00:52,216
But again, we work on a lot of other weird stuff, ranging from location

14
