You Fall, which is a melee combat action game with roguelite elements where you are a badass

18
00:01:15,377 --> 00:01:21,842
glowing knight fighting your way through a neon hellscape that kind of feels like it

19
00:01:21,882 --> 00:01:24,324
was taken from every 1980s album cover.

20
00:01:25,225 --> 00:01:31,810
And the core combat in the game is striving to be what we call like a rhythm light combat

21
00:01:31,890 --> 00:01:32,431
or gameplay.

22
